latestIgtvVideos.title: She wanted to share 🤍
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The smile on her face said so much. Even though she didn’t have much, she wasn’t only thinking of herself. She was thinking of others. 
The happiness on this child’s face is more than what I’ve seen on many folks today. She’s lives on the street. Imagine if you were in her shoes. I don’t think you would be smiling the way she is. I wish I had more on me tonight sadly I didn’t 💔 I hope our paths someday cross again 💓 
Give stop waiting to receive or you will wait your whole life. 
Until you know how to give, you will never appreciate when you receive💞 god bless her tonight. And all the other children around the world.
